videos.description: Zion Williamson drives between two defenders towards the basket for a layup.
videos.headline: Zion splits two defenders for layup

videos.description: RJ Barrett intercepts a pass and passes it to Zion WIlliamson, who quickly gives it to Javin DeLaurier for a layup.
videos.headline: Barrett's steal leads to layup

videos.description: Duke's Alex O'Connell comes up with a steal, breaks away to the basket and slams down a big two-handed jam.
videos.headline: O'Connell converts steal into dunk

videos.description: RJ Barrett knocks down a 3-pointer and on the very next possession, Alex O'Connell feeds Barrett for a breakaway dunk.
videos.headline: Barrett gets buckets on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Alex O'Connell is off the mark with a 3-pointer, but Jack White flies in for a putback dunk before the halftime buzzer sounds.
videos.headline: White gets putback dunk just before the half

videos.description: RJ Barrett passes the ball to Zion Williamson, who quickly finds his way to the basket for the layup.
videos.headline: Zion gets to the bucket for the easy finish

videos.description: Cam Reddish comes up with a steal and passes ahead to RJ Barrett, who elevates for a monster jam.
videos.headline: Barrett breaks away for hammer dunk

videos.description: RJ Barrett passes ahead to a driving Zion Williamson, who elevates for a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Zion rises up to throw it down
